member.summary: [MS-WMF] 2.1.1.2 BinaryRasterOperation Enumeration The BinaryRasterOperation Enumeration section lists the binary raster-operation codes. Rasteroperation codes define how metafile processing combines the bits from the selected pen with the bits in the destination bitmap. Each raster-operation code represents a Boolean operation in which the values of the pixels in the selected pen and the destination bitmap are combined.
